x-servers.description: OData APIs for the SuccessFactors Data Centers

info.title: Income Tax Declaration
info.description: API to access income tax declaration records and submit tax declarations actuals. It is also used to categorize or group investment types, configure the window period that controls the creation of actuals and proposals.
